{"markdown":{"yaml":{"title":""},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d6a4f 0%, #52b788 60%, #74c69d 100%); border-radius: 10px; padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 2rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; color: white; margin-bottom: 2rem;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; right:2rem; top:50%; transform:translateY(-50%); opacity:0.12; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; font-size:52px; color:white;\">\n    🌿 🐟 🌊\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; margin-bottom:14px;\">\n    🌱 Quantitative Ecologist & Applied Statistician\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:22px; font-weight:500; margin:0 0 6px;\">Baptiste Alglave</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin:0 0 18px;\">Associate Professor · Université Bretagne Sud · Lab-STICC (UMR 6285)</p>\n  <div style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n    <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">📍 Species distribution</span>\n    <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">📊 Spatio-temporal statistics</span>\n    <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">📈 Population dynamics</span>\n    <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">🌊 Marine ecosystems</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n:::: {.columns}\n::: {.column width=\"75%\"}\n\nI am a quantitative ecologist and applied statistician, with a specific interest in species distribution, population dynamics and spatio-temporal statistical modeling. I work at University Bretagne Sud as an associate professor of statistics (IUT Vannes, Data Science department) in the GIS group of Lab-STICC (UMR 6285).\n\nYou'll find additional details in the following pages!\n\nIf you want to contact me, here is:\n\n- **my email:** baptiste.alglave@univ-ubs.fr\n\n- **my current work address:** 8 Rue Michel de Montaigne, 56000 Vannes\n\n:::\n::: {.column width=\"5%\"}\n\n:::\n::: {.column width=\"20%\"}\n<center>\n![](ressource/images/baptiste_alglave.jpg)\n\n<a href=\"ressource/pdf/cv_baptiste_alglave_short.pdf\" style=\"color:#d0d3d4;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Short CV</a>\n\n<a href=\"ressource/pdf/cv_baptiste_alglave.pdf\" style=\"color:#d0d3d4;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Long CV</a>\n\n</center>\n:::\n::::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d6a4f 0%, #52b788 60%, #74c69d 100%); border-radius: 10px; padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 2rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; color: white; margin-bottom: 2rem;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; right:2rem; top:50%; transform:translateY(-50%); opacity:0.12; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; font-size:52px; color:white;\">\n    🌿 🐟 🌊\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; margin-bottom:14px;\">\n    🌱 Quantitative Ecologist & Applied Statistician\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:22px; font-weight:500; margin:0 0 6px;\">Baptiste Alglave</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin:0 0 18px;\">Associate Professor · Université Bretagne Sud · Lab-STICC (UMR 6285)</p>\n  <div style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n    <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">📍 Species distribution</span>\n    <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">📊 Spatio-temporal statistics</span>\n    <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">📈 Population dynamics</span>\n    <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">🌊 Marine ecosystems</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n:::: {.columns}\n::: {.column width=\"75%\"}\n\nI am a quantitative ecologist and applied statistician, with a specific interest in species distribution, population dynamics and spatio-temporal statistical modeling. I work at University Bretagne Sud as an associate professor of statistics (IUT Vannes, Data Science department) in the GIS group of Lab-STICC (UMR 6285).\n\nYou'll find additional details in the following pages!\n\nIf you want to contact me, here is:\n\n- **my email:** baptiste.alglave@univ-ubs.fr\n\n- **my current work address:** 8 Rue Michel de Montaigne, 56000 Vannes\n\n:::\n::: {.column width=\"5%\"}\n\n:::\n::: {.column width=\"20%\"}\n<center>\n![](ressource/images/baptiste_alglave.jpg)\n\n<a href=\"ressource/pdf/cv_baptiste_alglave_short.pdf\" style=\"color:#d0d3d4;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Short CV</a>\n\n<a href=\"ressource/pdf/cv_baptiste_alglave.pdf\" style=\"color:#d0d3d4;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Long CV</a>\n\n</center>\n:::\n::::\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":